<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.2.2">
<l>ōṭā vāḷariyi ṉuruvāyma ruviyeṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>māṭē vantaṭiyēṉ maṉaṅkoḷḷa vallamaintā</l>
<l>pāṭēṉ toṇṭartammaik kavitaippa ṉuvalkoṇṭu</l>
<l>nāṭē ṉuṉṉaiyallāl naṟaiyūrniṉ ṟanampīyō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Young man who is able to capture the mind of this servant, me,</l>
<l>Coming, appearing at my side in the form of a unretreating man-lion,</l>
<l>I do not sing of servants, adhering to prosodic texts;</l>
<l>I do not seek [anyone] but you, O noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
